headline: Illinois Tool Works (ITW): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Illinois Tool Works trades at $258.77 and has moved in lockstep with the market. Its shares have returned 9% over the last six months while the S&P 500 has gained 9.7%.
